>https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗衡中國魔掌<br />\n組建香港既遊說團隊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=a57511fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=319ded82\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"05bdd7cced8925f3ac012badc3e5d046c12d9760","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"推比 g phone"},{"pid":"fd0e886497b5db5fff4c6fffc68c363454222050","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"194f3f92d290bec95c42a479922f93800fecc789","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64d68997194bb09f0e2d46d99e973ab6fe8f1828","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:47:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d8511c211c95f5673168d8ff605acc2fd020b0a","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17f8f7251d5cb7351ce5b3152d89df97c5649ec4","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58c143dbad04e2fde11540b706d3ec00f314d00b","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"090d8eef52dbda93a756e0ece4b7632a79c46e5d","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6081241df9a5a6cc06bbaa166ef4e9444d506f94","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cc0ed1a91a04e2b174c088c524e84cb68ec4f1c5","tid":1672640,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid